        <mxCell id="4qypV36ItCKHLNTgIOiQ-14" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fontSize=12;fillColor=#fad9d5;strokeColor=light-dark(#2D7600,#660033);strokeWidth=7;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 19px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Alber the Abhartach – Final Fight&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Location Change:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Eire → Hidden Experimental Site in Laghtaverty&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Reason:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Key item: Saorise discovers research notes tied to red book in New Ossory and can’t help but investigate&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;o&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;It is in her nature to help people as seen with the banshees, the giant and cu Chulainn&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Encounter: Conditional boss fight&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Permanent death achieved&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Encounter: Dullahan Appearance&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Observes Alber’s “true death”&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Story Beat:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Saorise learns about King Brians experiments and the true horrors he will bring if he gets the real Raudskinna from Alber in his last moments&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt; Alber taunts her in his last moments claiming they are the same, shes just the light side and hes the dark side of the same coin&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;o&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Talking about her beast nature and ruthlessness in fights when fighting for what she believes&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;o&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Also talking about his artificially given powers and her naturally granted powers which both are on the brink of being godlike&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;o&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Saorise learns from Alber that her powers are not given by the gods, they just exposed her to them after her awakening(like finding out you can twitch your ears for the first time)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Wolf-men followed her to Laghtaverty and convince her to help&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="466.5" width="361" x="200" y="3760" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
